VERSATIL SDLC Framework - Additional Terms and Acknowledgments

This software includes the following components and methodologies:

1. BMAD (Business-Managed Agile Development) Methodology
   - Developed by the VERSATIL team
   - Licensed under MIT License

2. Agent-Based Development Framework
   - Six specialized AI agents: Maria-QA, James-Frontend, Marcus-Backend,
     Sarah-PM, Alex-BA, and Dr.AI-ML
   - Licensed under MIT License

3. Chrome MCP Integration
   - Integration with Model Context Protocol for browser testing
   - Chrome MCP is subject to its own licensing terms

4. Quality Gates Framework
   - Automated quality assurance and testing protocols
   - Licensed under MIT License

5. Context Preservation System
   - Zero-context-loss agent handoff system
   - Licensed under MIT License

Third-party dependencies are subject to their respective licenses:
- Node.js and npm packages used in this project
- Browser testing frameworks (Playwright, Chrome MCP)
- Development tools and utilities

For questions regarding licensing or commercial use, please contact:
support@versatil-platform.com

